{"lemma":"ظَلَمَة","slug":"ظَلَمَة","root":"ظ.ل.م","root_slug":"ظ-ل-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ظ-ل-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"ظالِم","root":"ظلم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":129},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27638","n27647","n27648","n27649"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B8%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"active participle of ظَلَمَ (ẓalama)","tags":["active","form-of","participle"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"active participle of ظَلَمَ (ẓalama); unjust; tyrannical, oppressing, iniquitous","examples":[{"text":"وَدَخَلَ جَنَّتَهُ وَهُوَ ظَالِمٌ لِّنَفْسِهِ قَالَ مَا أَظُنُّ أَن تَبِيدَ هَٰذِهِ أَبَدًا","english":"And he entered his garden while he was unjust to himself. He said, \"I do not think that this will perish - ever."}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of ظَلَمَ (ẓalama)."},"ipa":["/ðˤaː.lim/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27638","headword_ar":"ظلّمهُ","root":"Zlm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taZoliymN","text_ar":"تَظْلِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, &c.,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He told him that he was"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaAlim","text_ar":"ظَالِم"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"doing wrong"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acting wrongfully"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wrongdoer"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (T:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he attributed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"imputed, to him"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zulom","text_ar":"ظُلْم"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wrongdoing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (S, M, Msb, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a judge)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exacted justice for him from his wronger, and aided him against him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.)"}],"source_refs":["T"]},{"entry_id":"n27647","headword_ar":"ظُلْمَةٌ","root":"Zlm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulumapN","text_ar":"ظُلُمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K) [accord. to the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomN","text_ar":"ظُلْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulumN","text_ar":"ظُلُمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", both of which are wrong,] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalomaA='u","text_ar":"ظَلْمَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Darkness; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuwrN","text_ar":"نُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nonexistence of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuwr","text_ar":"نُور"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"light"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an accidental state that precludes the coëxistence therewith of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuwr","text_ar":"نُور"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Er-Rághib, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"departure of light;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalaAmN","text_ar":"ظَلَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K;) which last has no pl.; (T, TA;) or this last signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beginning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first part, of night,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"even though it be one in which the moon shines;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and is said by Sb to be used only adverbially; one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayotuhu ZalaAmFA","text_ar":"اَتَيْتُهُ ظَلَامًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I came to him at night,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEa AlZ~alaAmi","text_ar":"مَعَ الظَّلَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at the time of the night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomapN","text_ar":"ظُلْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulamN","text_ar":"ظُلَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulumaAtN","text_ar":"ظُلُمَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulamaAtN","text_ar":"ظُلَمَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomaAtN","text_ar":"ظُلْمَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) or, accord. to IB, the first of these pls. is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomapN","text_ar":"ظُلْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the second is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulumapN","text_ar":"ظُلُمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) One says, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yaxobiTu AlZ~alaAma","text_ar":"هُوَ يَخْبِطُ الظَّلَامَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlZ~alaAmi","text_ar":"فِى الظَّلَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", expl. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xbT","text_ar":"خبط"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~ulomapa","text_ar":"الظُّلْمَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which means the same] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~alomaA='a","text_ar":"الظَّلْمَا=ءَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is also expl. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xbT","text_ar":"خبط"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomapN","text_ar":"ظُلْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also [tropically] used as a term for (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ignorance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"belief in a plurality of gods:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"transgression,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unrighteousness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuwrN","text_ar":"نُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used as a term for their contraries: (Er-Rághib, TA:) and it is said in the A that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~ulomu","text_ar":"الظُّلْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomapN","text_ar":"ظُلْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEadolu","text_ar":"العَدْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuwrN","text_ar":"نُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulumaAtu AlbaHori","text_ar":"ظُلُمَاتُ البَحْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The troubles, afflictions, calamities,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hardships, of the sea."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)       -A2-  And one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN ZulomapN","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ ظُلْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [using the latter word as an epithet, (in the CK, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalimapN","text_ar":"ظَلِمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN ZalomaA='u","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ ظَلْمَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", both meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A night intensely dark;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) or the latter means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muZolimapN","text_ar":"مُظْلِمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dark,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"black"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolN ZalomaA='u","text_ar":"لَيْلٌ ظَلْمَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, (M, K,) which is anomalous, (K,) mentioned by IAar, but [ISd says] this is strange, and in my opinion he has put"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolN","text_ar":"لَيْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in his mentioning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolN qamoraA='u","text_ar":"لَيْلٌ قَمْرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (M.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulamN","text_ar":"ظُلَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": ―         -b3-  and see the paragraph next preceding it."}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n27648","headword_ar":"ظِلْمَةٌ","root":"Zlm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"sing. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZilamN","text_ar":"ظِلَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zil~aAmN","text_ar":"ظِلَّامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n27649","headword_ar":"ظُلُمَةٌ","root":"Zlm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZulomapN","text_ar":"ظُلْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}